de.tu_dresden.psy.inference.regexp

Class RegExpInferenceMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tu_dresden.psy.inference.regexp.RegExpInferenceMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InferenceMap

    public class RegExpInferenceMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements InferenceMap
    implements inference on String-Assertions via regular expressions (the name parameter is the only information used to check for equality!)
    Author:
    albrecht
